<section class="bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

      <!-- Left: Text -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-amber-700">
          Our Story
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-amber-700/90">
          <p>
            Nestled in the heart of the White Mountains of New Hampshire, our family has been
            crafting pure maple syrup for three generations. What started as a small hobby in
            our grandfather's backyard has grown into a labor of love that we're proud to share
            with families across New England.
          </p>
          <p>
            Each spring, when the sap begins to flow, you'll find us in our sugarhouse in
            Littleton, tending the wood-fired evaporator just as our grandparents did before us.
            We believe that the best maple syrup comes from patience, tradition, and a deep
            respect for the land that provides for us.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every bottle we produce is a testament to our commitment to quality over quantity.
            We tap only our own trees, fire the evaporator with sustainably harvested hardwood,
            and never rush the process. The result is a rich, complex maple syrup that captures
            the essence of a New Hampshire spring.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Image -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <img
          src="/maple-trees.webp"
          alt="Maple sap buckets hanging on sugar maple trees in early spring in the New Hampshire forest"
          class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover"
          style="max-height: 520px;"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>